      <title>3 月份投资者从对冲基金撤资 99 亿美元 - Nasdaq eVestment</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/investors-pull-99-bln-hedge-funds-march-nasdaq-evestment-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克 eVestment 周一发布的一份报告称，3 月份投资者从对冲基金净撤资额估计为 99 亿美元，高于 2 月份的 7.8 亿美元，这也是连续 22 个月行业资金流出总额超过资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/investors-pull-99-bln-hedge-funds-march-nasdaq-evestment-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 18:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
